primus (121031-1) precise; urgency=low

  * Automatically detect correct library from colon-separated path:
    - colon-paths.patch: make primus accept colon-separated paths.
    - rules: remove fixup and merge different PRIMUS_libGLa paths.
    - ubuntu_libgl_path.patch: do not always set nvidia in PRIMUS_libGL
      because it conflicts with nouveau.

